OL,3,CBank of England keeps interest rates
OL,4,Cunchanged at 5.25%
OL,6,FThe (BoE) has announced it has kept
OL,7,Funchanged at 5.25%.
OL,9,FIn 2024 the UK economy is expected to
OL,10,Fgrow by 0.5% and 1% next year -
OL,11,Fslightly higher than previous
OL,12,Fpredictions - the central bank's
OL,13,FMonetary Policy Committee (MPC) added.
OL,15,FThe decision means a longer period of
OL,16,Fhigher borrowing costs, which have
OL,17,Fsqueezed households since interest
OL,18,Frates started rising at the end of
OL,19,F2021.
