OL,6,FInterest rates inform us how high the
OL,7,Fcost of borrowing is, or high the
OL,8,Frewards are for saving.
OL,10,FMillions of people around the UK are
OL,11,Faffected by interest rates as they
OL,12,Finfluence mortgages, credit card and
OL,13,Fsavings rates.
OL,15,FThe BoE will raise interest rates to
OL,16,Fcurb high inflation, and the same is
OL,17,Ftrue for when inflation is low.
